SELECT id, title, concat('https://idyoveanwiuwcvgxijtz.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/eagle-images/', storage_path) AS imageUrl
FROM eagle_images
WHERE (title ILIKE '%lake%' OR '%lake%' = ANY(SELECT unnest(tags)))
   OR (title ILIKE '%door%' OR '%door%' = ANY(SELECT unnest(tags)))
   OR (title ILIKE '%threshold%' OR '%threshold%' = ANY(SELECT unnest(tags)))
   OR (title ILIKE '%water%' OR '%water%' = ANY(SELECT unnest(tags)))
ORDER BY created_at DESC, random()
LIMIT 3
